<div id="v150.2.7"><span class="H1121 s">The children</span><span class="H5867 s"> of Elam</span><span class="H505 s">, a thousand</span><span class="H3967 s"> two hundred</span><span class="H2572 s"> fifty</span><span class="H702 s"> and four</span>.</div>
