<div id="v150.2.10"><span class="H1121 s">The children</span><span class="H1137 s"> of Bani</span><span class="H8337 s">, six</span><span class="H3967 s"> hundred</span><span class="H705 s"> forty</span><span class="H8147 s"> and two</span>. <span class="notes">Notes by the 1611 King James Bible Translators: (Bani: or, Binnui)</span></div>
<div id="v150.2.11"><span class="H1121 s">The children</span><span class="H893 s"> of Bebai</span><span class="H8337 s">, six</span><span class="H3967 s"> hundred</span><span class="H6242 s"> twenty</span><span class="H7969 s"> and three</span>.</div>
