<div id="v150.2.24"><span class="H1121 s">The children</span><span class="H5820 s"> of Azmaveth</span><span class="H705 s">, forty</span><span class="H8147 s"> and two</span>. <span class="notes">Notes by the 1611 King James Bible Translators: (Azmaveth: or, Bethazmaveth)</span></div>
