<div id="v150.2.26"><span class="H1121 s">The children</span><span class="H7414 s"> of Ramah</span><span class="H1387 s"> and Gaba</span><span class="H8337 s">, six</span><span class="H3967 s"> hundred</span><span class="H6242 s"> twenty</span><span class="H259 s"> and one</span>.</div>
<div id="v150.2.27"><span class="H582 s">The men</span><span class="H4363 s"> of Michmas</span><span class="H3967 s">, an hundred</span><span class="H6242 s"> twenty</span><span class="H8147 s"> and two</span>.</div>
