<div id="v150.2.34"><span class="H1121 s">The children</span><span class="H3405 s"> of Jericho</span><span class="H7969 s">, three</span><span class="H3967 s"> hundred</span><span class="H705 s"> forty</span><span class="H2568 s"> and five</span>.</div>
